cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.TL, cs.SE, cs.LG

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a logical system with exponentials and fixpoints. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses the modelling of PCF (a programming language) using the logical system. 
- cs.TL (Theoretical Computer Science) is another possible category as the paper deals with the study of multitoken interaction machines and their properties. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the implementation of interactive semantics. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the least likely category as the paper does not mention any machine learning techniques or applications.
